ai.grakn.graph.internal

Class AbstractGraknGraph<G extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Graph>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.grakn.graph.internal.AbstractGraknGraph<G>
  • Type Parameters:
    G - A vendor specific implementation of a Tinkerpop Graph.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraknGraph, GraknAdmin, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GraknOrientDBGraph, GraknTinkerGraph, GraknTitanGraph

    public abstract class AbstractGraknGraph<G extends org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Graph>
extends Object
implements GraknGraph, GraknAdmin

    The Grakn Graph Base Implementation

    This defines how a grakn graph sits on top of a Tinkerpop Graph. It mostly act as a construction object which ensure the resulting graph conforms to the Grakn Object model.

    Author:
    fppt
